00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:27,400
I'll put them in for about ten minutes, I think.

396
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:30,480
They're only little, so they shouldn't take too long.

397
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:37,600
Right...

