00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:56,800
but one of the eggs is for painting egg on the top at the end.

404
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:58,600
I'm going to re-do it.

405
00:21:58,600 --> 00:22:01,360
30 minutes! Well, you wanted it basic.

