00:23:03,040 --> 00:23:05,160
Just keep patching.

420
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:08,600
Just keep patching, mate, it'll all be good.

421
00:23:08,600 --> 00:23:11,040
Keep patching. What could go wrong? They're just tarts.

